#User Story: HU-016
#title: Family Collaboration Rewards

Feature: Family Collaboration Rewards
    As a parent
    I want the app to reward our joint actions
    So that I can keep us motivated

Scenario: Earning a Collaboration Reward
    Given the parent registers a series of completed joint challenges
    When they reach the established threshold
    Then the system will award a special family badge
    And unlock new content
    And display a celebration animation
